{"tid":1766180,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方：如局勢持續惡化　憂慮會令謀殺　強姦案增加","createTime":"2019-12-02T11:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T16:23:03.000Z","uid":14328,"like":21,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"3bf8150110377946ace3eddf541588234b618bac","tid":1766180,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T11:29:38.000Z","msg":"昨日土瓜灣發生金行劫案，報道指當時警方正忙於應付在尖沙咀及紅磡一帶的遊行活動及示威事件，劫匪趁亂「博大霧」。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，今個月搶劫案有上升趨勢，與街頭巡邏的警力減少有關，擔心若情況持續，其他暴力罪行，例如謀殺、強姦等情況亦會惡化。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會議員葛佩帆博士稱，警方過去半年要動用大量警力遏止暴徒惡行，前線警員疲於奔命。警方由於擔心同袍在街上落單會有危險，改為接報後派警車到場，令街上巡警減少。<br />\n<br />\n葛博士指民建聯也是受害者，多個辦事處遭暴徒大肆破壞，被搶走電腦等財物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2019/12/02/345924/i_255x170_204204571.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2019%2F12%2F02%2F345924%2Fi_255x170_204204571.jpg&h=6f224f5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4cb2e97fdbeed53fc1095b629dae999611b3cfe","tid":1766180,"uid":140056,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T11:31:45.000Z","msg":"怪就怪政府"},{"pid":"92d24cdddee8cc4ad863050f521c9d59edb86624","tid":1766180,"uid":78947,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T11:32:26.000Z","msg":"辦事不力，扣人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0d473ae700de2557625031022e933ea7c4ee8a","tid":1766180,"uid":45672,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T11:32:49.000Z","msg":"即係再示威就捉人去姦。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9291961a0193a0e0d6b0275c29ae46afd76ff8e","tid":1766180,"uid":82640,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T11:33:16.000Z","msg":"擔憂警察強姦女扣留人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3763730fdfa762028938eb61f850df885644ddd","tid":1766180,"uid":235875,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"